title: Gorgeous two bedroom, 2 bath penthouse with spacious layout
posting_body: ['$%#%Gorgeous two bedroom, 2 bath penthouse with spacious layout and 10’ ceilings; brand-new finishes including kitchen with Italian granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances, imported porcelain tile flooring in wood grain finish, walk-in closets in both bedrooms and balcony with panoramic east views.', 'Full size washer and dryer in unit.', 'Master bath has dual sinks and roman tub.', '2 covered parking spaces included.', 'Building features luxury amenities including 24/7 concierge, fitness center, pool, recreational lounge, valet parking and is steps from Brickell City Center, Mary Brickell Village, restaurants and much more.%$&&', '#$%If you have been denied an application for lease in the past due to bad credit or your background, please call me or text me', 'show contact info', ', I will get you approved!!', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
